Package: StatsBombR
Type: Package
Title: Cleans and pulls StatsBomb data from the API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Derrick Yam
Maintainer: Derrick Yam <Derrick.Yam@statsbombservices.com>
Description: This package is used to pull StatsBomb data directly from the API. Currently, this is only supported on Windows computers since pulling functions use parallel computing.
